posts.raw_content:
While Obama being awarded it made the Nobel Prize a participation trophy, let’s be factual and not repeat lies that Trump was cheated in 2025.

January 31, 2025 is the submission cutoff date for the 2025 Nobel Peace Prize. For 2025, this deadline passed before the announcement on October 10, 2025.. Committee members could add names at their first meeting on February 26, 2025.

Trump will be eligible for the 2026 Nobel Peace Prize.

If he goes even further and secures peace between Russia and Ukraine prior to January 31, 2026 then it’s almost a shoe in. If not, no one will be at all surprised.  

In the end the real prize is Donald J. Trump Making America Great Again.
